name: Marian Ryan
articles__title: Middlesex District Attorney Marian Ryan Launches New Task Force to Address Incidents of Hate and Bias
articles__summary: Task force comprised of lawmakers, mayors, faith leaders, educators and youth leaders, community advocates and law enforcement created to address incidents of hate, concerning George Floyd/ the BLM movement, and anti-semitism

name: Rachael Rollins
articles__title: Suffolk DA Rachael Rollins releases list of police officers with ‘questionable’ credibility
articles__summary: Suffolk County District Attorney Rachael Rollins Friday night released a list of 136 area police officers who have been accused of misconduct, corruption, or other problematic behavior that would disrupt their credibility as witnesses in the court room.
